{"iti77:0.1":"Itivuttaka 77 ","iti77:0.2":"Tikanipata ","iti77:0.3":"Tatiyavagga ","iti77:0.4":"Bhidurasutta ","iti77:1.1":"Vuttanhetam bhagavata vuttamarahatati me sutam: ","iti77:2.1":"“Bhidurayam, bhikkhave, kayo, vinnanam viragadhammam, sabbe upadhi anicca dukkha viparinamadhamma”ti. ","iti77:2.2":"Etamattham bhagava avoca. ","iti77:2.3":"Tatthetam iti vuccati: ","iti77:3.1":"“Kayanca bhiduram natva, ","iti77:3.2":"Vinnananca viragunam; ","iti77:3.3":"Upadhisu bhayam disva, ","iti77:3.4":"Jatimaranamaccaga; ","iti77:3.5":"Sampatva paramam santim, ","iti77:3.6":"Kalam kankhati bhavitatto”ti. ","iti77:4.1":"Ayampi attho vutto bhagavata, iti me sutanti. ","iti77:4.2":"Atthamam. "}